719284f-a.title: Manhattan: Delancey Street - Clinton Street
719284f-a.text:
Delancey Street, north side, west from Clinton to Norfolk Streets.
Loew's Delancey Theatre, is at the N.W. corner of Suffolk Street.
February 12, 1937.
P. L. Sperr.
The 6-story structure partially shown on the right.is to be replaced
by a 1-story business building according to the Times of May 3, 1938.
This bears Nos. 156-164 Delancey Street and No. 10722Clinton Street; being
at the N.W. corner of same.
